data.description: **Seller Credit Offered for closing costs and upgrades!**This beautiful home is located in Anderson just off the I-5 Riverside exit. It sits on nearly a 10,000 sqft. corner lot in a quiet family neighborhood. Only a block away from the Tree Of Life Elementary School. Detached garage with a hot-water mud room, laundry hookups and a re-built work shop with new shelving & work bench. This beautiful home also offers a covered breezeway between the side entrance and garage, a newly roofed back patio, and RV parking.This home isn't short on outdoor beauty either, with it's large wrap around yard that offers newly landscaped lavender fern beds, a rainbow rose garden, pink magnolias, and shady oak trees.As well as summers filled with fruit from yellow plums, to grapes, avocados and blackberries. The inside offers ceiling fans throughout, stunning original hardwood floors, original cedar closets, newer dual-pane storm windows and a newly upgraded ice cold ducted cooler. This wonderful home was recently painted inside and out and has ample storage and great curb appeal!
